Designed by Greennix.  I hope others enjoy and can use this to make their own creations.

The on off buttons:
1. bluetooth connection(my PS3 controller)
2. Wired connection
3. Wifi Connection
4. OpenVPN running w/ external IP to verify

The script is ugly, I had issues with the pie_chart.lua loading font and other minor issues, so it may act strange when modified.

Items used/modified:

Wallpaper - http://kde-look.org/content/show.php?content=51146
Icons - Http://kde-look.org/content/search.php
      - PS3 Sixaxis http://www.iconarchive.com/show/playstation-3-icons-by-nendomatt/PS3-sixaxis-icon.html 
      - OPENVPN Icon - http://openvpn.net/index.php/miscellaneous/473-openvpn-logos-and-icons.html

Lua Script for pie chart - http://wlourf.deviantart.com/art/Pie-Chart-Widget-for-Conky-3-166109474

Font - http://www.urbanfonts.com/fonts/monofur.htm